-set superuser password
 sudo passwd root

Step 3. Enable ssh
crate empty "ssh" file in boot
Step 4. Add Network Info

    country=BY
    ctrl_interface=DIR=/var/run/wpa_supplicant GROUP=netdev
    update_config=1

    network={
       ssid="NETWORK-NAME"
       psk="NETWORK-PASSWORD"
    }
    Call the file wpa_supplicant.conf and save it